        "creation_date": 1625921447,
        "body": "<p>Try like this:<\/p>\n<pre><code>@RunWith(PowerMockRunner.class)\n@PrepareForTest(ClassUnderTest.class)\npublic class SimpleTest {\n\n    @Test\n    public void test() throws Exception {\n        ClassUnderTest underTest = new ClassUnderTest();\n\n        ClassName obj = new ClassName();\n\n        PowerMockito.whenNew(ClassName.class).withNoArguments().thenReturn(obj);\n\n        WhiteboxImpl.invokeMethod(underTest, &quot;getFunctReturn&quot;);\n    }\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
